name: James Wilton
description: I am kind and nice Guy. I am sociable and cheerful. I am very friendly to people and I like pleasant communication with intelligent and interesting people. I am humorous and optimist. I am also romantic, tender and passionate man. I am very sensible and touchable. And I try to avoid rude people.In my free time I like to be going for sport – jogging, doing exercises, I like to read books, cooking my favorite dishes, watching movies. I have many flowers in my house, I like animals.
